Si Sari ang girlfriend ko.

259
00:15:02,300 --> 00:15:03,967
Ay, tama na!

260
00:15:03,967 --> 00:15:06,733
I'm so excited to meet you.

261
00:15:06,733 --> 00:15:08,133
Ikinagagalak din kitang makilala, Sari.

262
00:15:08,133 --> 00:15:09,733
[SARI] Ikinagagalak din kitang makilala.

263
00:15:09,733 --> 00:15:16,667
["SILONG KA MUNA" CONTINUES]

264
00:15:23,133 --> 00:15:26,500
