274
00:16:04,367 --> 00:16:05,667
[LIQUID TRACKLING]

275
00:16:07,533 --> 00:16:08,800
Kaya...

276
00:16:09,567 --> 00:16:12,500
sa hitsura nito,
Hindi yata naging maganda.

277
00:16:16,567 --> 00:16:17,667
[HINGA NG MALALIM]

278
00:16:18,767 --> 00:16:20,533
Sabihin mo sa akin ang tungkol dito
