279
00:16:21,733 --> 00:16:25,200
[UUMAUWI ANG MGA HAKBANG]

280
00:16:30,867 --> 00:16:33,700
- [LIQUID TRCKLING]
- [GULPING]

281
00:16:33,700 --> 00:16:36,367
[MOROSE MUSIC CONTINUES]

282
00:16:36,367 --> 00:16:38,533
[HINGA NG MALALIM]

283
00:16:40,633 --> 00:16:42,700
Alam ko, Uncle,
maraming

284
00:16:42,733 --> 00:16:45,333
isla resort hotel
sa Pilipinas.

285
00:16:45,333 --> 00:16:47,433
Ngunit kung ano ang gumagawa
Iba't ibang Hotel 88

286
00:16:47,433 --> 00:16:50,600
ay talagang ito ay isang pagtakas
mula sa buhay lungsod.

287
00:16:50,600 --> 00:16:53,833
