288
00:16:53,833 --> 00:16:55,367
Narinig ko na yan Martin.

289
00:16:56,267 --> 00:16:57,533
Iba ang local vibes.

290
00:16:58,400 --> 00:17:00,767
Luho ng isla
ang tawag natin dito.

291
