293
00:17:09,733 --> 00:17:12,133
Oo, sir. Ipinanganak at lumaki.

294
00:17:12,900 --> 00:17:14,467
Anong ginagawa mo, Sari?

295
00:17:15,633 --> 00:17:16,833
Ay, Tiyo...

296
00:17:17,800 --> 00:17:20,633
Ako ay isang mabuting pakikitungo
