303
00:17:35,600 --> 00:17:36,767
[WHISPERS] Gold flakes.

304
00:17:37,533 --> 00:17:39,767
- Ginto sa ice cream! Fancy!
- Shh!

305
00:17:42,200 --> 00:17:45,433
Uh, ibig kong sabihin,
ice cream ang paborito ko.

306
00:17:46,933 --> 00:17:48,633
Sari. Sari, mas maliliit na kagat,
pakiusap.

307
00:17:48,667 --> 00:17:49,800
Baka sobrang lamig.

308
00:17:50,967 --> 00:17:52,867
[MAMAHIMONG HUMANGKOL si SARI]

309
00:17:56,000 --> 00:17:58,500
[MARTIN]
Sari, Sari, wag kang dumura--

310
00:17:58,500 --> 00:18:00,667
Huwag mong isubo.
Matunaw naman.

311
00:18:00,667 --> 00:18:02,833
- Sari, Sari--
- [SARI HUNGKOL]

312
00:18:02,833 --> 00:18:04,300
Huwag mong isubo.

313
00:18:06,000 --> 00:18:08,500
- Sari...
- [PAGPATULOY ANG HUMANGKOL]

314
00:18:08,500 --> 00:18:10,833
Bigyan mo siya ng tubig.
Uminom ka ng tubig, Sari.

315
00:18:10,833 --> 00:18:13,700
Paumanhin. Hindi sanay si Sari sa ganito.

316
00:18:13,700 --> 00:18:15,167
Kumuha ng tubig.

317
00:18:16,367 --> 00:18:18,767
Alam ba ni Carlos
na ganito ang ginagawa mo dito?

318
00:18:20,967 --> 00:18:25,633
[SARI HUMINGA NG MABILIS]

319
00:18:28,267 --> 00:18:29,867
Sari, pakiusap. Uminom ng mas maraming tubig.

320
00:18:29,867 --> 00:18:31,933
