321
00:18:31,933 --> 00:18:33,367
Cheers, tao!

322
00:18:33,367 --> 00:18:35,367
Enjoy na lang tayo ha?

323
00:18:35,367 --> 00:18:37,867
Tara na guys.
Happy hour na!

324
00:18:37,867 --> 00:18:38,833
[WOMAN] Ay!

325
00:18:38,833 --> 00:18:41,033
[TENSE MUSIC PLAYING]

326
00:18:41,033 --> 00:18:42,900
Hoy, saan ka pupunta?

327
00:18:42,900 --> 00:18:44,400
Kumuha ka muna!

328
00:18:45,367 --> 00:18:47,667
Halika, guys, mag-shot tayo.

329
00:18:47,667 --> 00:18:49,333
Nasa akin na. babayaran ko ito.

330
00:18:49,333 --> 00:18:51,233
Sir, sir, alam ko ang pakiramdam na ito.

331
00:18:51,233 --> 00:18:53,333
lasing ka na.
Sapat na ang nainom mo.

332
00:18:53,333 --> 00:18:54,900
Hindi ako lasing.
Nagsasaya lang ako.

333
00:18:54,900 --> 00:18:56,667
Pwede bang wag mong sirain ang gabi ko?

334
00:18:57,700 --> 00:18:59,067
Miss, shots tayo.

335
00:18:59,067 --> 00:19:00,367
- Argh!
- Sir!

336
00:19:01,633 --> 00:19:03,267
Tama na, okay?

337
00:19:03,267 --> 00:19:04,400
Ano bang problema mo?

338
00:19:04,400 --> 00:19:06,467
- Tama na!
- Gusto ko lang ng mga shot!

339
00:19:06,467 --> 00:19:08,367
- Ano? Huwag mo akong hawakan!
- Hindi mo ako kilala.

340
00:19:08,367 --> 00:19:09,400
Bakit ang yabang mo?

341
00:19:09,400 --> 00:19:10,900
- Gusto mo ng mas maraming shot?
- Nagsasaya lang ako!

342
00:19:10,900 --> 00:19:13,967
Justin! Justin! Chase! Chase!
Tama na.

343
00:19:13,967 --> 00:19:16,067
Ito ay isang hotel, hindi ba?
Hindi ko ba ma-enjoy ang oras ko?

344
00:19:16,067 --> 00:19:17,900
Tanga mo! Hindi ito ang iyong bahay!

345
00:19:17,900 --> 00:19:20,400
- Tama na.
- Miss, pwede bang maki-shot?

346
00:19:20,400 --> 00:19:21,933
Justin, tama na.
Hayaan mo akong hawakan ito.

347
00:19:21,933 --> 00:19:24,433
- Kakausapin ko siya!
- Bigyan mo ako ng isang shot, mangyaring.

348
00:19:24,433 --> 00:19:25,867
Chase, tama na!

349
00:19:25,867 --> 00:19:27,867
Wala ka sa Manila!
Kumuha ng isang mahigpit na pagkakahawak!

350
00:19:35,000 --> 00:19:36,600
Alam mo,

351
00:19:36,600 --> 00:19:38,567
