ang ice cream ko noon.

396
00:21:46,033 --> 00:21:47,933
Hindi ko na natapos kasi
Sobrang kaba ang naramdaman ko.

397
00:21:48,067 --> 00:21:49,833
[NAKATANGI]

398
00:21:49,933 --> 00:21:52,333
Sige po sir.

399
00:21:52,433 --> 00:21:54,700
