ilang ice cream sa susunod.

400
00:21:54,800 --> 00:21:56,700
May ginawa kaming ice cream
mula sa niyog.

401
00:21:56,800 --> 00:21:58,500
Maaaring wala ito
gold flakes, pero...

402
00:21:58,600 --> 00:22:00,767
